oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Rites of Spring (2004)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Festivals; Music festivals; Keen, Robert Earl; Rouse, Josh; Dirty Dozen Brass Band; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (blue on orange) announcing Rites of Spring 2004 featuring Talib Kweli, The Wailers, North Mississippi All Stars, Robert Earl Keen, Flickerstick, Josh Rouse, Dirty Dozen Brass Band, OK Go, Marc Broussard, Jag Star, Jimmy Hall and the Prisoners of Love, Dan Darrah Band, Jedd Hughes The Someday Tour, Monte Montgomery, Matt Wertz, The Whigs, Mieka Pauley, The Loft, and Christopher Robin at Vanderbilt University in Nashville, Tennessee on April 22-23. Poster features woodcuts of stars and music notes.
